quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,Haa-Meeem
  45,2,is kitaab ka utaara jana khuday-e ghalib ( aur ) Dana ( ki taraf ) se hai
  45,3,be shak asmano aur zameen mein imaan walon ke liye ( khuda ki qudrat ki ) nishanain hain
  45,4,aur tumhari paidaiesh mein bhi. aur janwaron mein bhi jin ko woh phelata hai yaqeen karne walon ke liye nishanain hain
  45,5,aur raat aur din ke agay peechay anay jaane mein aur woh jo khuda ne aasman sezarya rizaq nazil farmaya phir is se zameen ko is ke mrjane ke baad zindahkiya is mein aur hawaon ke badalny mein aqal walon ke liye nishanain hain
  45,6,yeh khuda ki ayatain hain jo hum tum ko sachaai ke sath parh kar sunaate hain. to yeh khuda aur is ki aayton ke baad kis baat par imaan layein ge ?
  45,7,har jhutay gunehgaar par afsos hai
  45,8,( ke ) khuda ki ayatain is ko parh kar sunai jati hain to un ko sun to laita hai ( magar ) phir ghuroor se zid karta hai ke goya un ko suna hi nahi. so aisay shakhs ko dukh dainay walay azaab ki khushkhabri suna do
  45,9,aur jab hamari kuch ayatain usay maloom hoti hain to un ki hansi urata hai. aisay logon ke liye zaleel karne wala azaab hai
  45,10,un ke samnay dozakh hai. aur jo kaam woh karte rahay kuch bhi un ke kaam nah ayen ge. aur nah wohi ( kaam ayen ge ) jin ko unhon ne khuda ke siwa mabood bana rakha tha. aur un ke liye bara azaab hai
  45,11,yeh hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) hai. aur jo log apne perwar-digaar ki aayton se inkaar karte hain un ko sakht qisam ka dard dainay wala azaab hoga
  45,12,khuda hi to hai jis ne darya ko tumahray qaboo kardiya taakay is ke hukum se is mein kashtiyan chalein aur taakay tum is ke fazl se ( muaash ) talaash karo aur taakay shukar karo
  45,13,aur jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab ko apne ( hukum ) se tumahray kaam mein laga diya. jo log ghhor karte hain un ke liye is mein ( qudrat khuda ki ) nishanain hain
